            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Yaaay, we got a big victory.<CR>Ahem!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Niooo! I'm so glad you're safe!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x138,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's wrong, Sis? You look so pale."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Are you hurt anywhere?<CR>Did anything happen to you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Umm, I think I'm okay.<CR>Sis, you worry too much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but I might've scrapped my knee a bit..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Hold on! I'll put on some ointment and a bandage right now!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Jeez, I'll be fine. You're overreacting, Sis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "No, it could get infected and turn into something much worse."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "C'mon now, drink this medicine.<CR>You'll feel better right away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "And put on some of this ointment...<CR>And put on this medical patch..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x138,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Wh-Wh-Wh‐! I don't need all that medicine..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I'm better than fine! See!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "R-Really? If you say so..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But let me know right away if it starts to hurt when you're walking, okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I'm totally confident about my medicine, so I'll make sure you won't feel any pain right away!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Sis, isn't that kinda scary...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Did I say something weird?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Goodness, there's no help for you, Sis. Come on, let's just keep on going."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Nio! It's dangerous to run!"
